Install: Throttle Concurrent Builds Plugin

Configure Throttle Concurrent Builds for Pipeline Jobs:
Manage Jenkins-->System-->Throttle Concurrent Builds-->Multi-Project Throttle Categories-->Add Category-->Name(any_name)-->Maximum Total Concurrent Builds(1)-->Maximum Concurrent Builds Per Node(1)-->SAVE

Apply Throttle Configuration to Jobs:
Go to your Pipeline configuration-->Throttle Concurrent Builds-->Select(Throttle this project as part of one or more categories)-->Maximum Total Concurrent Builds(1)-->Maximum Concurrent Builds Per Node(1)-->SAVE and RUN
